    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">3–12</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The G tile adds 2 points and creates strong consonant clusters. Words like WRECKAGE and BLOCKAGE pair -AGE with the CK combo (C=3, K=5) for instant high scores. The suffix is also defensive — longer -AGE words are hard to extend further.</p>

